Name: Don't Get Tagged
About the game: Overview Play through 20 levels of difficult puzzles, enemies and obstacles within their respected zones, Let nothing get in your way and get to the goal! Just don't get tagged in the process. Gameplay This game is an isometric top down point and click strategy game focused on your movement, placement and exciting movement. Features 20 Levels to play. Two zones with unique environments. Three difficulties modes. Timekeeping and leaderboard mechanics Behind the project Hello my name is Lewis and this is indeed my first game. This project has been an entire learning experience and have been working on it for over an year and has been my passion project of mine. This is only a stepping stone and hope to do bigger and better projects in the future.
